<BLOCK1><TI TOCID="I">NOTICE OF APPEAL</TI>
<P><BOLD>THE APPELLANTS</BOLD> appeal to the Court of Appeal for Ontario from the Judgment/ Order of the Honourable Mr. Justice McLean, dated May 19, 2016, at Ottawa, Ontario.</P>
<P><BOLD>THE APPELLANT ASKS</BOLD> that:
<P1>(a) the Judgment/Order of the Honourable Mr. Justice McLean, dated May 19, 2016 be set aside, in part;</P1>
<P1>(b) leave to appeal be granted with respect the costs of all proceedings below;</P1>
<P1>(c) costs of the appeal on a substantial indemnity scale; and</P1>
<P1>(d) such further and other relief as to this Honourable Court seems just.</P1></P>
